\par }\pard \s29 \qj\sb180\fi360 {\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\v0\expnd0\expndtw0\outl0\shad0\f0\fs24\cf0\nosupersub (7.5) (a) "Special needs offender" means a person in the custody of the department:
\par }\pard \s29 \qj\sb180\fi360 {\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\v0\expnd0\expndtw0\outl0\shad0\f0\fs24\cf0\nosupersub (I) Who is sixty years of age or older and has been diagnosed by a licensed health care provider who is employed by or under contract with the depa
