\par }\pard \s29 \qj\sb180\fi360 {\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\v0\expnd0\expndtw0\outl0\shad0\f0\fs24\cf0\nosupersub (I) Was convicted of a class 1 felony, unless the offense was committed before July 1, 1990, and the offender has served at least twenty years in a
