\par }\pard \s29 \qj\sb180\fi360 {\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\v0\expnd0\expndtw0\outl0\shad0\f0\fs24\cf0\nosupersub (II) Was convicted of a class 2 felony crime of violence as described in section 18-1.3-406, C.R.S., and the offender has served fewer than ten yea
rs in a department of corrections facility for the offense.
