te of the warden's decision. Geerdes v. Colo. Dept. of Corr., 226 P.3d 1261 (Colo. App. 2010).
\par }\pard \s8 \qj\sb180\sa180\fi360 {\*\bkmkstart 17-1-204}{\*\bkmkend 17-1-204}{\b\fs24 17-1-204. Background checks.
