te compact.
\par }\pard \s29 \qj\sb180\fi360 {\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\v0\expnd0\expndtw0\outl0\shad0\f0\fs24\cf0\nosupersub (4) and (5) (Deleted by amendment, L. 2000, p. 839, \'a7 24, effective May 24, 2000.)
