\par }\pard \s29 \qj\sb180\fi360 {\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\v0\expnd0\expndtw0\outl0\shad0\f0\fs24\cf0\nosupersub (a) To promulgate rules governing the granting and revocation of parole, including special needs parole pursuant to section 17-22.5-403.5, from cor
