\par }\pard \s29 \qj\sb180\fi360 {\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\v0\expnd0\expndtw0\outl0\shad0\f0\fs24\cf0\nosupersub (b) To promulgate rules for the conduct of board members, the procedures for board hearings, and procedures for the board to comply with state fisc
