\par }\pard \s29 \qj\sb180\fi360 {\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\v0\expnd0\expndtw0\outl0\shad0\f0\fs24\cf0\nosupersub (d) To adopt a policy pursuant to which the board may conduct parole hearings, parole revocation hearings, and board meetings using video teleconfe
rencing technology. At a minimum, the policy shall identify:
