on of the department of corrections or the board, and the victim of the crime or relative of the victim, if the victim has died, has the duty to keep the department of corrections or the board informed of his or her most current address.
\par }\pard \s29 \qj\sb180\fi360 {\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\v0\expnd0\expndtw0\outl0\shad0\f0\fs24\cf0\nosupersub (b) In the case of any offenses other than offenses against the person as specified in article 3 of title 18, C.R.S., notice of any parole proceedi
