in the facility operated by the department of human services shall continue to be charged to the department of human services.
\par }\pard \s29 \qj\sb180\fi360 {\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\v0\expnd0\expndtw0\outl0\shad0\f0\fs24\cf0\nosupersub (2) (Deleted by amendment, L. 2000, p. 846, \'a7 43, effective May 24, 2000.)
