\par }\pard \s29 \qj\sb180\fi360 {\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\v0\expnd0\expndtw0\outl0\shad0\f0\fs24\cf0\nosupersub (1) There is hereby created in the department of corrections the division of correctional industries, which shall be under the direction of the dir
