\par }\pard \s29 \qj\sb180\fi360 {\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\v0\expnd0\expndtw0\outl0\shad0\f0\fs24\cf0\nosupersub (II) Four members of the general assembly, two of whom shall be appointed by the speaker of the house of representatives and two of whom shall be a
