ointed in January at the beginning of the regular session held in odd-numbered years and shall serve through the legislative biennium.
\par }\pard \s29 \qj\sb180\fi360 {\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\v0\expnd0\expndtw0\outl0\shad0\f0\fs24\cf0\nosupersub (III) The director of the office of state planning and budgeting;
