\par }\pard \s29 \qj\sb180\fi360 {\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\v0\expnd0\expndtw0\outl0\shad0\f0\fs24\cf0\nosupersub (1) The division shall establish programs which are responsible for physical plant and facility maintenance, vehicle maintenance, and food and laun
dry services for each of the state's correctional facilities, and providing license plates and highway signs for the state.
\par }\pard \s29 \qj\sb180\fi360 {\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\v0\expnd0\expndtw0\outl0\shad0\f0\fs24\cf0\nosupersub (2) All staff members, authorized full-time equivalent employees, capital equipment, and inventories currently used for physical plant maintenance 
