\par }\pard \s29 \qj\sb180\fi360 {\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\v0\expnd0\expndtw0\outl0\shad0\f0\fs24\cf0\nosupersub (3) All vocational training programs, personnel, inventories, and equipment shall be resources dedicated to the establishment of the correctional i
ndustries program.
\par }\pard \s29 \qj\sb180\fi360 {\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\v0\expnd0\expndtw0\outl0\shad0\f0\fs24\cf0\nosupersub (4) A portion of the real property at each correctional institution shall be designated by the executive director as an industry area, and all faci
lities and buildings within this area shall be assigned to the division in cooperation with the division of adult parole. The responsibility for the maintenance and upkeep of these facilities, buildings, and grounds shall be vested in the division.
\par }\pard \s9 \qj {\v\fs8 History
