\par }\pard \s29 \qj\sb180\fi360 {\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\v0\expnd0\expndtw0\outl0\shad0\f0\fs24\cf0\nosupersub (7) The administrator of any community corrections program established pursuant to this section shall notify a referring agency immediately that an
