n the offender cannot be safely housed in the community corrections program.
\par }\pard \s29 \qj\sb180\fi360 {\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\v0\expnd0\expndtw0\outl0\shad0\f0\fs24\cf0\nosupersub (8) Upon placement of an offender in a community corrections program, the administrator of the program shall notify local law enforcement agencies 
