\par }\pard \s29 \qj\sb180\fi360 {\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\v0\expnd0\expndtw0\outl0\shad0\f0\fs24\cf0\nosupersub (11) The administrator of each community corrections program shall report to the division of criminal justice and the community corrections board o
