\par }\pard \s29 \qj\sb180\fi360 {\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\v0\expnd0\expndtw0\outl0\shad0\f0\fs24\cf0\nosupersub (12) The administrators of a community corrections program established pursuant to this section may implement a mental illness screening program to
