\par }\pard \s29 \qj\sb180\fi360 {\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\v0\expnd0\expndtw0\outl0\shad0\f0\fs24\cf0\nosupersub (a) "Director" means the director of the department's community corrections program and whose powers and duties include those of a community correc
