\par }\pard \s29 \qj\sb180\fi360 {\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\v0\expnd0\expndtw0\outl0\shad0\f0\fs24\cf0\nosupersub (1) (a) If an offender fails to remain within the extended limits of such offender's confinement or placement or fails to return within the time pr
