\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\v0\expnd0\expndtw0\outl0\shad0\f1\fs20\cf0\nosupersub  and he acknowledged advisement of the contents of this residential curfew directive in writing, the directive constituted an extended limitation of defendant's confinement. People 
v. Williams, 33 P.3d 1187 (Colo. App. 2001); People v. Perea, 74 P.3d 326 (Colo. App. 2002).
