statute and the intensive supervision program (ISP) statute.}{\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\v0\expnd0\expndtw0\outl0\shad0\f1\fs20\cf0\nosupersub  In an escape case, the court must make a factual determination whether a defendant was placed in home detention or ISP
