hority to assign a defendant to the regimented inmate training program (RITP), a trial court does not exceed its authority by making a recommendation to the department}{\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\v0\expnd0\expndtw0\outl0\shad0\f1\fs20\cf0\nosupersub  or simply b
