te to the healing and improved emotional well-being of their victims.
\par }\pard \s29 \qj\sb180\fi360 {\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\v0\expnd0\expndtw0\outl0\shad0\f0\fs24\cf0\nosupersub (2) The purpose of this article is to encourage the establishment of programs to provide for restitution to and restoration of victims of crime by 
