\par }\pard \s29 \qj\sb180\fi360 {\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\v0\expnd0\expndtw0\outl0\shad0\f0\fs24\cf0\nosupersub There is hereby created in the state treasury the correctional education program fund, which shall be administered by the program and that shall co
